'''黛安娜·蓋伯頓'''（{{lang-en|Diana Gabaldon}}，{{bd|1952年|1月11日}}），是一位[[美国|美国]][[作家|作家]]、[[小說家|小說家]]，最著名的作品是《異鄉人》（{{le|Outlander (book series)|Outlander}}）系列小说。她的作品合并多个流派，具有历史，浪漫，神秘，冒险，科幻，奇幻元素<ref name="EW Devils">{{cite web|last=Reese|first=Jennifer|title=Book Review: ''Lord John and the Hand of Devils'' (2007)|website=[[Entertainment_Weekly|Entertainment Weekly]]|url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20162421,00.html|date=November 27, 2007|accessdate=October 30, 2013|archive-date=2014-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141011020739/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20162421,00.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《異鄉人》改编的电视劇《[[古戰場傳奇|-{zh-hans:古战场传奇; zh-tw:異鄉人：古戰場傳奇; zh-hk:古戰場傳奇}-]]》在2014年首演<ref name="HR 2014-05-08">{{cite web |url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/outlander-premiere-date-poster-revealed-702417 |title=Starz's ''Outlander'' Gets First Poster, Premiere Date |first=Philiana |last=Ng |work=[[The_Hollywood_Reporter|The Hollywood Reporter]] |date=May 8, 2014 |accessdate=June 14, 2014 |archive-date=2019-03-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190328164714/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/outlander-premiere-date-poster-revealed-702417 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="EW 2nd Season">{{cite web |url=http://insidetv.ew.com/2014/08/15/outlander-renewed-second-season/ |title=''Outlander'' renewed for second season |work=Entertainment Weekly |first=James |last=Hibberd |date=August 15, 2014 |accessdate=August 15, 2014 |archive-date=2015-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150118183114/http://insidetv.ew.com/2014/08/15/outlander-renewed-second-season/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

